vious one. It doesn=E2=80=99t=C2=A0matter=C2=A0for getting the deal done; M=
usk is committed for the full $33.5 billion, and he has the money. Maybe he=
=E2=80=99ll do it alone, or maybe he=E2=80=99ll do it with the $7.1 billion=
 he raised from his friends in April and May, or maybe they=E2=80=99ll aban=
